{"tid":1990332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★太古城3房戶成交　持貨13年賬面賺近1200萬元","createTime":"2020-04-26T15:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T15:05:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81c19638b476294d442d878d0fe1b5117d2d7c68","tid":1990332,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"藍籌屋苑太古城再錄減價成交。美聯吳肇基指出，屋苑銀柏閣高層E室，實用面積922平方呎，為三房連套房間隔，原業主於去年10月以1,925萬元放盤，最終獲用家以1,830萬元承接，累減95萬元，折合實用呎價為19,848元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2007年1月以638萬元購入該單位，持貨13年賬面賺1,192萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/465488/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E6%B8%9B%E5%83%B995%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD-%E5%8E%9F%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%A813%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%AC%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA%E8%BF%911200%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F465488%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A5%25973%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2583%25B995%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25B2%25BD-%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25B2%25A813%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25AC%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E8%25BF%25911200%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4B5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=762a4969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/465488/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E6%B8%9B%E5%83%B995%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD-%E5%8E%9F%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%A813%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%AC%E9%9D%A2%E8%B3%BA%E8%BF%911200%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83</a>"},{"pid":"f364d7d7d64fc2d58dd48e5d3e40e9ba47aa5e73","tid":1990332,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T15:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.